author: By Joseph Curtis For Mailonline
description: Meghan Markle has arrived in the UK ahead of Pippa Middleton's wedding this weekend, with the actress, 35, said to have been quickly whisked from Heathrow to Kensington Palace.
title: Meghan Markle lands in UK ahead of Pippa's wedding

author: By Joseph Curtis For Mailonline
description: Prince Harry would be able to marry girlfriend Meghan Markle at Westminster Abbey despite her being a divorcee, the Church of England has confirmed.
title: Prince Harry CAN wed Meghan Markle at Westminster Abbey

author: By Ephraim Hardcastle for the Daily Mail
description: While Prince Harry’s girlfriend, actress Meghan Markle, has yet to meet the Queen, a royal source insists: ‘They are not engaged formally but there is an understanding,' writes EPHRAIM HARDCASTLE.
title: EPHRAIM HARDCASTLE: Will Harry pop the question in August?
